studyDesigns.name: Study Design
studyDesigns.rationale: Protocol-defined study design for investigating efficacy and safety

arms.name: iRESTORE Illumina LED Treatment
arms.description: Participants use iRESTORE Illumina LED Face Mask and iRESTORE Illumina LED Neck & Chest Mask for 10 minutes daily in the evening for 12 weeks. Face mask uses Mode 1 for all sessions.

eligibilityCriteria.name: Willingness to avoid new skin health products
Willingness to avoid direct sun exposure
Diagnosed skin condition with recent flare-up
History of skin cancer or precancerous lesions
Pregnant, breastfeeding, or trying to conceive
Recent or planned invasive medical procedure
Allergic reaction to aluminum or plastics
History of seizures or epilepsy triggered by light
History of carotid artery disease or related conditions
Recent discontinuation of hormonal birth control

objectives.name: Primary Objective
objectives.text: To evaluate changes in overall skin appearance, as measured by dermatologist skin grading.

objectives.name: Secondary Objective
objectives.text: To assess changes in a range of skin health parameters.

endpoints.name: Improvement in Skin Appearance
endpoints.text: Improvements in skin health parameters will be evaluated by dermatologist grading at Baseline and Week 12.

endpoints.name: Improvement in Skin Health Parameters
endpoints.text: Improvement in skin plumpness, fine lines and wrinkles, pigmentation, tone and texture, redness, firmness, elasticity, radiance, and appearance of crepey skin. Participant perceptions of skin health will be evaluated through subject-specific questionnaires at Baseline, Week 2, Week 4, Week 6, Week 8, Week 10, and Week 12.

studyInterventions.name: iRESTORE Illumina LED Face Mask
studyInterventions.description: LED face mask utilizing 360 LEDs to provide firmer, smoother, and clearer skin through light therapy

studyInterventions.name: iRESTORE Illumina LED Neck & Chest Mask
studyInterventions.description: LED neck and chest mask utilizing 230 LEDs to provide firmer, smoother, and clearer skin through light therapy
